race.description: Affinity Constructions Country Boosted Maiden Plate
race.comment: COLORADO SUN (7) pushed forward third-up with a gritty on-pace second over 1400m at Canberra. Cherry ripe for this and can get off the mark at start five. GUNFIGHTER ROAD (8) returns from a lengthy break on his home track. Solid debut when he closed late to run second over 1400m at this track last September. Winkers go on and returns without a trial. Expected to go close. INNA ZOU (12) gave away a big start and never looked a genuine contender with a plugging fifth over 1400m at Canberra. Finds a weaker contest and placed here earlier in the prep. Value chance. OCEANSIDE (4) looking for this trip and further now after he caught the eye late in the heavy (9) going with a respectable fourth over 1100m at this track. Claim helps again and not to be overlooked. WIRE TO WIRE (6) fitter now and has minor place claims.
